{"tid":2372054,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金世正澄清緋聞後 隔空合體世勛谷新節目","createTime":"2021-01-19T10:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T12:08:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1de0af44003650b3bbaab5bdb96eccd4171684","tid":2372054,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4geOlIaMwcgObMi3wK-gC45kjak=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JXIPA6PIJZE5ZNY6DKO7YANPXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4geOlIaMwcgObMi3wK-gC45kjak%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJXIPA6PIJZE5ZNY6DKO7YANPXE.jpg&h=67fcd270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNetflix首個原創韓國綜藝節目《Busted!韓星齊鬥智》已拍到第三季，今季除了「國民MC」劉在錫、EXO成員世勛、朴敏英、金世正、李昇基等舊成員繼續出演外，第二季沒有演出的李光洙在第三季中再度與眾人合體。<br />\n<br />\n周五開播<br />\n而《Busted!韓星齊鬥智3》將於本周五開播，雖然金世正日前就開直播澄清與同節目的世勛的緋聞，並無奈表示連父母都遭到惡評，令她大感傷心，但就無損她今日收拾心情為節目做宣傳。金世正因為大熱《驅魔麵館》而人氣急升，她亦十分識做，事前在IG公開靚相造勢。金世正表示知道自己的作品上了Netflix的排行榜，亦令到她獲得不少海外fans的支持及私訊，她開心說：「我感受到了節目在海外的反應都好好。」<br />\n<br />\n公開海報<br />\n由於受疫情影響，節目今日就進行連線網上發佈會，一眾演出演員都各自介紹節目，緋聞男女金世正和世勛亦隔空合體。同時節目組亦有公開最新花絮照及海報，第三季將增加了犯罪驚悚的元素，令眾人要想盡方法破案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/svz1EvpIVdvNHFC-IlE-v5fRZxw=/802x787/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YCDI7QFPTJGFPD3W6IL2BGGUO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsvz1EvpIVdvNHFC-IlE-v5fRZxw%3D%2F802x787%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYCDI7QFPTJGFPD3W6IL2BGGUO4.jpg&h=c6493f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ylADyoXtPCVvFUCJelgTKhFT4ps=/802x319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GGH2ANSKTVALZH3I